    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's still basically giving me insulin when i haven't eaten. honestly i'm just really nervous about waking up at 3am with a massive hypoglycemic episode. if i just skip the basal dose tonight, my sugar should stay relatively stable because i'm not eating, right? it seems way safer to just skip it than to take any extra insulin when i'm this empty.",
